entries.journal_entry_description: Ehartt Brihnt will test your hunting abilities by asking you to hunt wallugas in Etyyy.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Go speak with Ehartt Brihnt at the primary Rodian hunting camp.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Ehartt wants you to collect 21 perfect walluga claws. Any wallugas in Etyyy could have them.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: You've collected the perfect walluga claws. Now return to Ehartt at the main Rodian hunting camp.
